  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tonight, a supernova is set to explode in the sky – a rare event that Eli and Lum are eager to witness together through their homemade telescope. But an accident sends the telescope tumbling from the roof, scattering its pieces across the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Determined not to miss this special moment, Eli sets out through the streets at night. Along the way, he talks to people, explores locations, collects items, and gradually reassembles the telescope.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As he wanders through the city, memories long buried begin to resurface.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short, story-driven point-and-click adventure about friendship, trauma, memories, and a night that changes everything.</p>",
